articles.title: Travis Kelce Heads Backstage as Taylor Swift Sings 'Karma Is the Guy on the Chiefs' During Amsterdam Show - PEOPLE
articles.description: Travis Kelce attended Taylor Swift's Eras Tour show in Amsterdam on Friday, July 5, and footage posted online from the concert shows him watching in the crowd and heading backstage as she nodded to him with altered lyrics in her song 'Karma.'
articles.content:
Travis Kelce knows how to make his mark at Taylor Swift's shows!
